public interface IHasID

An interface for UBY-LMF classes that have a unique identifier.

Method Detail

getId

java.lang.String getId()
Returns the unique identifier of the UBY-LMF object.

Returns:
the unique identifier of the UBY-LMF object or null, if the object does not have the identifier set

Note that all UBY-LMF classes implementing IHasID interface should have this field set. Absence of the value of identifier field may indicate to an incomplete conversion process of the original resource.
